content:
### Flex Alignment

Flexbox provides powerful alignment controls for both axes.

---

### Main Axis (justify-content)

```css
.container {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: flex-start;    /* Start (default) */
  justify-content: flex-end;      /* End */
  justify-content: center;        /* Center */
  justify-content: space-between; /* Even gap between */
  justify-content: space-around;  /* Gap around each */
  justify-content: space-evenly;  /* Equal gaps */
}
```

---

### Cross Axis (align-items)

```css
.container {
  display: flex;
  align-items: stretch;     /* Fill height (default) */
  align-items: flex-start;  /* Top */
  align-items: flex-end;    /* Bottom */
  align-items: center;      /* Middle */
  align-items: baseline;    /* Text baseline */
}
```

---

### Align Self (Individual Item)

```css
.item {
  align-self: auto;          /* Inherits from container */
  align-self: flex-start;    /* Top of cross axis */
  align-self: flex-end;      /* Bottom of cross axis */
  align-self: center;        /* Center of cross axis */
  align-self: stretch;       /* Stretch to fill */
  align-self: baseline;      /* Baseline alignment */
}
```

---

### Centering Everything

```css
.container {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
}
```

The classic "perfect centering" — centers content both ways.

---

### Align Content (Multi-line)

When `flex-wrap: wrap` creates multiple lines:

```css
.container {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  align-content: flex-start;    /* Lines at top */
  align-content: flex-end;      /* Lines at bottom */
  align-content: center;        /* Lines centered */
  align-content: space-between; /* Lines spaced */
  align-content: space-around;  /* Space around lines */
  align-content: stretch;       /* Lines stretch (default) */
}
```

---

### Alignment Cheatsheet

```css
/* Center everything */
.center {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
}

/* Right align */
.right {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: flex-end;
}

/* Bottom center */
.bottom {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: flex-end;
}

/* Spread apart, top */
.spread {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: flex-start;
}
```

> **Key Point:** `justify-content` = main axis. `align-items` = cross axis. `align-content` = cross axis for multi-line.
